\c 21
\s AbeGibeyoni bayaphindisela
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusiba khona indlala ensukwini zikaDavida iminyaka emithathu, umnyaka ngomnyaka ilandelana; uDavida wadinga ubuso beN\nd kosi\nd*. IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi: Kungenxa kaSawuli langenxa yendlu \add yakhe\add* yegazi, ngoba wabulala amaGibeyoni\x + 21.2. 1 Sam. 22.18,19.\x*.
\v 2 Ngakho inkosi yabiza amaGibeyoni yathi kuwo: (AmaGibeyoni-ke ayengeyisiwo awabantwana bakoIsrayeli, kodwa ayengawensali yamaAmori; njalo abantwana bakoIsrayeli babefungile kuwo; uSawuli wasedinga ukuwatshaya ekutshisekeleni kwakhe abantwana bakoIsrayeli loJuda\x + Josh. 9.3-17.\x*.)
\v 3 Ngakho uDavida wathi kumaGibeyoni: Ngingalenzelani? Ngingayenza ngani inhlawulo yokuthula ukuze libusise ilifa leN\nd kosi\x + 20.19. 1 Sam. 26.19.\x*\nd*?
\v 4 AmaGibeyoni asesithi kuye: Kayisindaba yesiliva kumbe igolide loSawuli lendlu yakhe; futhi kakusikwethu ukubulala umuntu koIsrayeli. Wasesithi: Lokho elikutshoyo ngizalenzela khona.
\v 5 Basebesithi enkosini: Umuntu owasiqedayo, owaceba emelene lathi ukuthi sichithwe singasali lakuwuphi umngcele wakoIsrayeli,
\v 6 kasinikwe amadoda ayisikhombisa emadodaneni akhe\x + Hlu. 20.5. Hlab. 50.21.\x*, njalo siwaphanyekele iN\nd kosi\nd* eGibeya kaSawuli, okhethiweyo weN\nd kosi\x + Josh. 18.28.\x*\nd*. Inkosi yasisithi: Mina ngiza\add li\add*pha.
\v 7 Kodwa inkosi yamyekela uMefiboshethi indodana kaJonathani indodana kaSawuli ngenxa yesifungo seN\nd kosi\nd* esasiphakathi kwabo, phakathi kukaDavida loJonathani indodana kaSawuli\x + 1 Sam. 20.8.\x*.
\v 8 Kodwa inkosi yathatha amadodana amabili kaRizipa indodakazi kaAya ayewazalele uSawuli\x + 3.7.\x*, uArimoni loMefiboshethi, lamadodana amahlanu \add kadadewabo\add* kaMikhali indodakazi kaSawuli ayewazalele uAdriyeli indodana kaBarizilayi umMehola,
\v 9 yabanikela esandleni samaGibeyoni, asebaphanyeka entabeni phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, njalo abayisikhombisa bawa kanyekanye. Babulawa ensukwini zokuvuna, \add ensukwini\add* zakuqala ekuqaleni kokuvunwa \w kwebhali\w**\x + Ruthe 1.22.\x*.
\p
\v 10 URizipa indodakazi kaAya wasethatha isaka, wazendlalela lona phezu kwedwala, kusukela ekuqaleni kokuvuna kwaze kwathonta amanzi phezu kwabo evela emazulwini; kavumelanga inyoni zamazulu ukuthi zihlale phezu kwabo emini, lezilo zeganga ebusuku\x + Dute. 21.23.\x*.
\v 11 Kwasekubikelwa uDavida lokho uRizipa indodakazi kaAya, umfazi omncane kaSawuli, ayekwenzile.
\p
\v 12 UDavida wasehamba wa\add ya\add*thatha amathambo kaSawuli lamathambo kaJonathani indodana yakhe kubahlali beJabeshi-Gileyadi\x + 2.4,5. Josh. 24.11.\x* ababewebile\x + 1 Sam. 31.10-13. Hlu. 21.8.\x* emdangeni weBeti-Shani, lapho amaFilisti ayebaphanyeke khona mhla amaFilisti etshaya uSawuli eGilibowa\x + Josh. 17.11.\x*.
\v 13 Wasesenyusa esuka lapho amathambo kaSawuli lamathambo kaJonathani indodana yakhe; basebeqoqa amathambo awababephanyekiwe.
\v 14 Basebewangcwaba amathambo kaSawuli lakaJonathani indodana yakhe elizweni lakoBhenjamini eZela\x + Josh. 18.28.\x*, engcwabeni likaKishi uyise. Benza konke inkosi eyayibalaye khona. Njalo emva kwalokho uNkulunkulu wancengeka ngenxa yelizwe\x + 24.25. Gen. 25.21.\x*.
\s Abantu bakaDavida babulala isiqhwaga
\p
\v 15 AmaFilisti abuye aba lempi futhi loIsrayeli; uDavida wasesehla lenceku zakhe kanye laye, njalo balwa lamaFilisti; uDavida wasedinwa.
\v 16 UIshibi-Benobi owayengowabantwana besiqhwaga, osisindo somkhonto wakhe sasing\add amashekeli\add* angamakhulu amathathu ethusi, wayebhince \add inkemba\add* entsha, wathi uzamtshaya uDavida\x + 18.11.\x*.
\v 17 Kodwa uAbishayi indodana kaZeruya wamsiza, wamtshaya umFilisti wambulala\x + 1 Sam. 26.6.\x*. Khona abantu bakaDavida bafunga kuye besithi: Kawusayikuphuma impi lathi, hlezi ucitshe isibane sikaIsrayeli\x + 18.3.\x*.
\v 18 Kwasekusithi emva kwalokhu kwaba lempi futhi lamaFilisti eGobi\x + 1 Lan. 20.4-8.\x*; khona uSibekayi\x + 23.27. 1 Lan. 4.4. 1 Lan. 27.11.\x* umHusha watshaya uSafi, owayengowabantwana besiqhwaga\x + 23.27. 1 Lan. 4.4. 1 Lan. 27.11.\x*.
\v 19 Kwasekusiba lempi futhi lamaFilisti eGobi; uElihanani indodana kaJahari-Oregimi umBhethelehema\x + 23.24.\x*, watshaya \add umfowabo ka\add*Goliyathi umGiti\x + 5.8. 1 Lan. 20.5.\x*, oluthi lomkhonto wakhe lwalunjengogodo lomaluki\x + 23.7. 1 Sam. 17.7.\x*.
\v 20 Njalo kwabuye kwaba lempi eGathi\x + 1 Sam. 17.4.\x*, lapho okwakulomuntu omude, owayeleminwe eyisithupha ezandleni zakhe, lamazwane ayisithupha ezinyaweni zakhe, \add kung\add*amatshumi amabili lane ngenani; laye-ke wayezalelwe isiqhwaga.
\v 21 Lapho eseyisa uIsrayeli, uJonathani indodana kaShimeya, umfowabo kaDavida, wamtshaya\x + 1 Sam. 16.9.\x*.
\v 22 Laba abane babezalelwe isiqhwaga eGathi; njalo bawa ngesandla sikaDavida langesandla senceku zakhe\x + 21.16,17.\x*.